go for the win?

05:53.020 --> 05:54.555
I don't know
who you think you talking to,

05:54.588 --> 05:56.390
but watch your tone with me.
Pop.

05:56.424 --> 05:59.827
I can't deal with my life
until you get this done.

05:59.860 --> 06:03.531
So you come with something
better, or let's close this.

06:06.434 --> 06:08.869
(door closes)

06:08.902 --> 06:12.573
That is a dangerous way to come
at our biggest investor, Pop.

06:12.606 --> 06:15.075
