it is not a rap battle.

06:15.108 --> 06:16.510
Oh, it's all the same to me,

06:16.544 --> 06:18.679
as long as I win
in the end of it.

06:18.712 --> 06:21.014
That's why you want
to humiliate Hakeem?

06:21.048 --> 06:23.517
So you can win
in the end?

06:23.551 --> 06:26.219
That's why you want to control
all of us? Not to teach us?

06:26.253 --> 06:28.522
Not to make us
better men?

06:28.556 --> 06:30.090
But just so you can
win in the end?

06:30.123 --> 06:31.692
Well, I think history has shown

06:31.725 --> 06:33.927
