39:30.402 --> 39:32.003
a stupid bet.

39:32.037 --> 39:34.406
We both put up
your next album.

39:34.440 --> 39:36.007
Look, look,
look, I know

39:36.041 --> 39:37.743
I didn't have the
right to do it, Hakeem,

39:37.776 --> 39:40.712
but at least you know
I have faith in you. Hmm.

39:43.281 --> 39:44.850
* Never loved us...

39:44.883 --> 39:47.085
Dad.

39:47.118 --> 39:50.188
I say this as someone who
loves you more than anything.

39:50.221 --> 39:52.357
Just let us have this moment.

39:52.390 --> 39:54.359
* Never loved us

39:54.392 --> 39:57.095
* Worst behavior...

39:57.128 --> 39:59.064
Excuse me, sir.
(talking quietly)

39:59.097 --> 40:00.365
* Never loved us

40:00.398 --> 40:01.867
* Worst behavior...

40:01.900 --> 40:03.134
No, don't let her in.

40:03.168 --> 40:06.905
No, no, matter of fact,
hold on. Uh-uh. Uh-uh.

40:06.938 --> 40:08.373
Hey, Cookie?

40:08.406 --> 40:09.374
COOKIE:
What?

40:09.407 --> 40:11.042
Your sister's here.

40:11.076 --> 40:13.044
Who, Carol?
No, the other one.

40:13.078 --> 40:14.379
CANDACE:
Loretha!

40:14.412 --> 40:15.714
Hey, hey, miss, come on, now.
Loretha!

40:15.747 --> 40:16.882
Loretha!

40:16.915 --> 40:19.217
It's important!
I need to talk to you!

40:19.250 --> 40:22.120
Loretha! It's important, girl!
I need to talk to you!
Who's that?

40:22.153 --> 40:24.255
Candace.

40:24.289 --> 40:26.558
Just... Excuse me.

40:26.592 --> 40:28.927
I said, get...
get your hands off of me!

40:28.960 --> 40:31.897
I told you, I need to
speak with my sister.

40:31.930 --> 40:33.732
Excuse me, fellas.
Thank you.
Yes.

40:33.765 --> 40:35.601
Thank you.

40:35.634 --> 40:37.435
Candace, can you not
show up around here

40:37.469 --> 40:39.104
acting like you at
the Cherry Hill Mall,

40:39.137 --> 40:40.105
embarrassing me?

40:40.138 --> 40:41.640
Oh, stop it.

40:41.673 --> 40:44.309
You know I wouldn't be
here if it wasn't serious.

40:44.342 --> 40:45.911
Oh, okay, well,
then what is it?

40:45.944 --> 40:48.079
Our sister is
on a bender.

40:48.113 --> 40:51.249
And? What she smoked
don't make me choke.

40:51.282 --> 40:54.486
Child, that's what you came
all the way up here to tell me?

40:54.520 --> 40:57.489
If 17 years of prison
taught you anything,

40:57.523 --> 40:59.925
it's definitely how to
dress like a monkey

40:59.958 --> 41:01.426
and talk like a pimp.

41:01.459 --> 41:03.261
It's our sister!
LUCIOUS: Look, hold on.

41:03.294 --> 41:05.130
You know, just when I thought

41:05.163 --> 41:08.767
nothing could make this night
get good, you showed up.

41:08.800 --> 41:10.536
Thank you.

41:12.538 --> 41:13.839
You're welcome, Lucious.

41:13.872 --> 41:15.774
(laughs)

41:15.807 --> 41:18.544
You know, I never did like
your fake ass, Candace.

41:20.979 --> 41:22.948
Yeah, you show up
around here like

41:22.981 --> 41:24.349
you all concerned
about Carol.

41:24.382 --> 41:26.151
I am.
No, you're not.

41:26.184 --> 41:29.788
The first thing you do is get
to talking slick out your mouth.

41:29.821 --> 41:31.456
Real greasy,

41:31.489 --> 41:34.459
looking down your nose at me
like you ain't from

41:34.492 --> 41:37.963
the same hood I'm from,
married to your white man.

41:37.996 --> 41:39.030
And he's rich.

41:39.064 --> 41:41.633
I can't tell
by them cheap-ass shoes.

41:41.667 --> 41:43.334
Okay.
If your bougie ass

41:43.368 --> 41:45.336
called your family
more often,

41:45.370 --> 41:48.540
maybe you'd know Carol ain't
nothing but a scammer.

41:48.574 --> 41:51.176
All she does is run game,
trying to scam

41:51.209 --> 41:52.377
a hot dollar.

41:52.410 --> 41:53.979
The only thing
that's new is that

41:54.012 --> 41:55.513
she got your number
instead of mine.

41:56.682 --> 41:58.016
Welcome back
to the family, Candace.

41:58.049 --> 41:59.985
She left her kids.

42:00.018 --> 42:02.053
What?
Yeah.

42:02.087 --> 42:04.690
She dumped them at
my house with a note,

42:04.723 --> 42:07.993
saying that this was all
Cookie and Jermel's fault.

42:08.026 --> 42:09.861
(sighs)

42:09.895 --> 42:11.529
What have you
done, Loretha?

42:14.199 --> 42:16.067
What have you done?!

42:16.101 --> 42:18.369
Look, come on.
We-we got to go to Philly.

42:18.403 --> 42:20.538
Philly?!
Yes, Philly!

42:20.572 --> 42:22.574
(Hakeem and Laura laugh)

42:24.542 --> 42:27.045
There go your car, babe.
I'll see you tomorrow.

42:29.547 --> 42:32.517
You sure you don't want me
to come home with you?

42:32.550 --> 42:34.185
Don't make that face.

42:34.219 --> 42:36.688
Yeah, I do, but I want to
make sure we right first.

42:36.722 --> 42:39.224
Okay.

42:46.064 --> 42:48.099
Be safe.

42:52.270 --> 42:53.705
ANIKA:
All right.

42:53.739 --> 42:55.707
Where to?

42:55.741 --> 42:58.276
163rd and Seventh.

42:58.309 --> 43:00.378
Got you.

43:00.411 --> 43:02.748
Buckle up.

43:42.187 --> 43:44.189
Yeah.

